    <h3>Building Blocks</h3>
    <p>The idea behind this Creation is to highlight different qualities of the espresso. Mixing walnut butter into the espresso enhances the nuttiness and mouthfeel. Then by sipping the espresso and cranberry juice alternately you get a kick of acidity to finish off.</p>
