    <h3>Peach Iced Tea</h3>
    <p>We have cold brewed Lalani &amp; Co Assam Gold 2nd Flush from the Belseri Estate. This black tea is delicate, clean and sweet. We have complemented its flavours by infusing it with ripe peaches.</p>

    <p>Lalani &amp; Co are family owned, have close relationships with their farmers and specialise in micro lot and small batch tea. The care they take and the amount of knowledge they have about tea is mind boggling.</p>
  </div>
