  <div class="col-md-8">
    <h3>"Coffee... but not as you know it" or Sparkling Cascara with Lime.</h3>

    <p>Cascara is the dried fruit of the coffee cherry and can be infused in hot water to make a fruity tea-like beverage. It usually ends up being discarded in the rush to get to those aromatic beans but it tastes AWESOME and is packed with caffeine!</p>

    <p>We've made a super strong Cascara reduction for the Creation, mixed with a splash of lime and sparkling water served over ice. This one will see us through summer with a bang.</p>
  </div>
