    <p>We featured this signature drink at the <%= link_to 'London Coffee Festival', 'http://www.londoncoffeefestival.com/trueartisancafe.aspx' %>.</p>
    <p>A delicious long black served with Sorrel oil, lemon and honeycomb. Herbaceously delicious. AND we have a secret, fun food pairing up our sleeve thanks to Bittersweet Bakers.</p>
    <p>MINI HONEY AND BASIL MERINGUES!</p>
