  <div class="col-md-8">
    <h3>East India Coffee</h3>
    <p>This is an espresso based drink, made with our house espresso. The shots are pulled ristretto style to obtain
    an intense sweet flavour to which we will then add 6 ounces of creamy
    steamed milk that has been infused for 48 hrs with warm spices of
    cardamon, cinnamon and star anise, along with vanilla, honey and
    ginger.</p>

    <p>Smooth, warm delicious and comforting. Perfect for winter weather.</p>
  </div>
</div>

