  <div class="col-md-8">
    <h3>Ginger and Chilli Brewed Coffee</h3>

    <p>The coffee we are using is a fully washed Ethiopian Sidamo. Brewed as
    a drip filter, sweet lemon is the dominant flavour that develops in
    the cup.  Combined with fresh ginger and a kick of chilli the resulting
    drink is warm and spicy with lots of lovely acidity. Delicious! Bonus
    points for being a tasty alternative to a milky latte, if you need to
    watch your waist line after Christmas and for containing natural
    goodness to ward off germs on the tube.</p>

  </div>
